name: Alan
description: I am Alan and I am Outreach Director for Coding With A Purpose. (I made this very jank website) I have been in this glorious club since 9th grade. Outside of CWAP, I am programming lead for Team 303, and I run for our school's track team.

name: Ayush
description: Hi everyone! My name is Ayush and I am the president of Coding With A Purpose. I have been in this club since freshman year, joining originally to gain experience in coding projects. This club has now grown to much more than just coding, I have met fascinating people, made lifelong experiences, and gotten to work on incredible meaningful projects.
